## Project conventions

- Date-prefix time-stamped artifacts (`YYYY-MM-DD-foo.md`)
- ADRs use numbered names (`NNNN-title.md`); per-feature ADRs have their own counter
- Plan revisions append-only at top; never rewrite history
- Feature docs travel with their branch — `docs/features/<feature>/` may exist on a feature branch but not on main
